
# Samsung Form Project Rules

## Project Overview
This is a modern Vue.js 3-based landing page application with an admin panel for form management. The project features a Samsung-inspired design system with dynamic form building capabilities and responsive design.

## Project Structure
```
samsung_form/
├── backend/                    # Node.js backend server
│   ├── server.js              # Main server file
│   └── setup.js               # Server setup and configuration
├── public/                     # Static assets
│   └── favicon.svg            # SVG favicon (preferred format)
├── src/                        # Vue.js frontend source
│   ├── components/             # Vue components
│   │   ├── admin/             # Admin-specific components
│   │   └── LandingForm.vue    # Main contact form
│   ├── pages/                 # Route components
│   ├── stores/                # Pinia state management
│   └── router/                # Vue Router configuration
├── index.html                  # Main HTML entry point
├── tailwind.config.js         # Tailwind CSS configuration
└── vite.config.ts             # Vite build configuration
```

**Note**: The `lov-app/` directory is ignored by `.gitignore` and contains a separate React application that is not part of the main project structure.

## Technology Stack

### Frontend (Main Project)
- **Vue.js 3** with Composition API
- **Vite** as build tool
- **Tailwind CSS** for styling
- **Vue Router** for client-side routing
- **Pinia** for state management
- **TypeScript** for type safety

### Backend
- **Node.js** server
- **Express.js** framework
- **Google Sheets API** integration (Google Drive functionality removed)

### Ignored Directories
- **`lov-app/`** - Separate React application (ignored by .gitignore)
- **`node_modules/`** - Dependencies (ignored by .gitignore)

## Design System

### Color Palette
- **Primary**: Blue accent (#3B82F6)
- **Background**: Pure white (#FFFFFF)
- **Foreground**: Near black (#0F0F23)
- **Muted**: Light gray (#F8F9FA)
- **Success**: Green (#16A34A)
- **Destructive**: Red (#DC2626)
- **Warning**: Orange (#F59E0B)

### Typography
- **Font Family**: Inter (Google Fonts)
- **Heading Scale**: text-5xl to text-7xl for hero sections
- **Body Text**: text-base with responsive scaling
- **Font Weights**: 400 (normal), 600 (semibold), 700 (bold)

### Component Variants
- **Button Variants**: btn-hero, btn-ghost, btn-dark
- **Form Components**: form-input, form-select
- **Card Variants**: card-modern, card-dark

### Animations
- **Fade In**: animate-fade-in
- **Scale In**: animate-scale-in
- **Slide Up**: animate-slide-up
- **Hover Effects**: hover-lift

## Coding Standards

### File Naming
- **Components**: PascalCase (e.g., `LandingForm.vue`)
- **Pages**: PascalCase (e.g., `Index.vue`)
- **Stores**: camelCase (e.g., `auth.ts`)
- **Utilities**: kebab-case (e.g., `utils.ts`)

